tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_engagement_metrics (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    content_id UUID,
    engagement_type VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    duration_seconds INT
)

CREATE TABLE user_engagement_metrics (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    content_id INT,
    engagement_level ENUM('low', 'medium', 'high'),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    duration_seconds INT
);

CREATE TABLE audience_behavior (
    audience_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    content_id INT,
    page_views INT,
    unique_visitors INT,
    rating FLOAT,
    comments TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE user_engagement (
    engagement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    content_id INT,
    engagement_type TEXT,
    engagement_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE audience_behavior (
    behavior_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    content_id INT,
    behavior_type TEXT,
    behavior_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE media_content (
   content_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   content_name VARCHAR(255),
   content_type VARCHAR(50),
   genre VARCHAR(50),
   release_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE UserEngagementMetrics (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    content_id UUID,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    engagement_type VARCHAR,
    rating INT
)

CREATE TABLE DigitalMediaContent (
    content_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR,
    category VARCHAR,
    duration INT,
    publication_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE UserProfiles (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR,
    email VARCHAR,
    registration_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE ContentAnalytics (
    content_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    total_views INT,
    unique_views INT,
    likes INT,
    shares INT
)

CREATE TABLE UserInteractions (
    interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    content_id UUID,
    interaction_type VARCHAR,
    interaction_date TIMESTAMP
)
